### Create Instructor 1

POST http://localhost:8080/instructors HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@uncg.edu",
  "name": "Alice Smith",
  "passwordHash": "alicehash",
  "role": "INSTRUCTOR"
}


